Package net.sf.tweety.arg.prob.lotteries

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgumentationLottery
    This class implements an argumentation lottery, i.e. a lottery on an exhaustive and disjoint set of divisions.
    LdoArgumentationLottery
    This class implements an argumentation lottery based on the logic of dialectical outcomes, i.e. a lottery on an exhaustive and disjoint set of formulas of LDO.
    LdoUtilityFunction
    A utility function that maps LDO formulas to utilities
    SubgraphProbabilityFunction
    Represents a probability function on the subgraphs of some Dung theory.
    UtilityFunction
    A utility function that maps divisions to utilities
